  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272730/extras/e7909f16070b8031ecc3ad64e4d5f101.avif?t=1763213471\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272730/extras_big/e7909f16070b8031ecc3ad64e4d5f101.avif?t=1763213471 width=800 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272730/extras/c0eeb40a879b38b500b77aafb3c864c0.webp?t=1763213471\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272730/extras_big/c0eeb40a879b38b500b77aafb3c864c0.webp?t=1763213471 width=800 height=7 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>Synopsis:</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>Whispers of Fear</strong>, you’re drawn into a chilling psychological horror experience. After fleeing from a mysterious stalker, the protagonist seeks refuge in her family’s house deep in the woods.<strong></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The false sense of security keeps pulling you into a tense and nerve-racking atmosphere. Every sound, every shadow will make you question what’s real. With an unexpected twist, you’ll need to figure out if you can escape or if the danger still lurks in the dark.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Perfect for players looking for an immersive, realistic experience, Whispers of Fear will leave you wondering if you're ever truly safe.</i><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272730/extras/c0eeb40a879b38b500b77aafb3c864c0.webp?t=1763213471\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272730/extras_big/c0eeb40a879b38b500b77aafb3c864c0.webp?t=1763213471 width=800 height=7 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>Gameplay:</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore and survive in a desolate atmosphere, in a house on the outskirts of a forest at dusk.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Progressive story as the days and nights unfold.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >First-person experience, exploration, suspense, horror.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Events based on the player's choices and actions.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immersive atmosphere and sounds.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Psychological horror, realism. A story that could happen in real life.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Retro setting.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The story progresses based on objectives.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272730/extras/c0eeb40a879b38b500b77aafb3c864c0.webp?t=1763213471\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272730/extras_big/c0eeb40a879b38b500b77aafb3c864c0.webp?t=1763213471 width=800 height=7 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
