ong><i>Gameplay:</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore and survive in a desolate atmosphere, in a house on the outskirts of a forest at dusk.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Progressive story as the days and nights unfold.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >First-person experience, exploration, suspense, horror.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Events based on the player's choices and actions.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immersive atmosphere and sounds.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Psychological horror, realism. A story that could happen in real life.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Retro setting.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The story progresses based on objectives.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272730/extras/c0eeb40a879b38b500b77aafb3c864c0.webp?t=1763213471\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272730/extras_big/c0eeb40a879b38b500b77aafb3c864c0.webp?t=1763213471 width=800 height=7 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
